snippet.title: ✅  Amber Heard joined by girlfriend Bianca Butti as she prepares for her final day of evidence in Jo
snippet.description:
💖 Please Visit: https://www.facebook.com/Scathc/
💖 Please Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMWjJ3knbjImE8pdNeB2Rfw?sub_confirmation=1
✍   Amber Heard was joined by girlfriend Bianca Butti as she prepared for her final day of evidence in ex-husband Johnny Depp’s libel trial.   Amber, 34, arrived at the High Court this morning in good spirits, waving to the camera and smiling.   The Aquaman actress wore a long black dress and the red polka dot scarf she has been using as a face-mask, and was followed into the building by her girlfriend Bianca.  Ms Butti wore a blue bandana around her face as she walked behind Amber, dressed in a black suit and a patterned shirt.    The cinematographer has been supporting Heard throughout the trial and has been pictured at the courts on numerous occasions, as well as being seen out and about with the actress in London after the daily sessions.    The couple were first linked together earlier this year, when they were pictured kissing in Palm Springs in January.  A source told Us Weekly: ‘Amber is fine and happier than ever.  ‘Bianca has been very supportive of her, and Amber feels like sh ...
💖
